  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Will the technique of adding lidocaine to bupivacaine fasten the onset of bupivacaine alone
      for infraclavicular brachial plexus block in end-stage renal disease (ESRD) patient?
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
